      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/2bfe46/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-10-29T18:36:41.416Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Sic e thote edhe titulli. Me shfletues te ndryshem peshku shfaqet ndryshe. Me FF 55+ and Chrome jam ne gjendje te shikoj kollonene kryesore plus ato djathtas (Letersi, Shtypi, Te fundit etj) me IE11, Opera 12.xx, kollonat djathtas nuk shfaqen. Pse?</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 57013,
      "post_number": 2,
      "username": "squarepusher",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/squarepusher/{size}/13677_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-10-29T18:45:36.283Z",
      "cooked": "<p>varet se cilin variant merr shfletuesi per ‘default’: pamjen per desktop apo pamjen per mobile. Gjithsesi ne te gjithe shfletuesit kete gje mund ta kontrollosh nga menuja si ne foton me poshte. mund ta nderrosh sipas preferences dhe kjo vlen per te gjithe shfletuesit.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76\" title=\"IMG_20171029_194052.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76_2_467x800.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20171029_194052\" width=\"467\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76_2_467x800.jpg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76_2_700x1200.jpg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76_2_934x1600.jpg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c1339ea03f7f8634243c09ce2f2fa6172dea4c76_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_20171029_194052.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×1849 207 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 57040,
      "post_number": 3,
      "username": "Patrioti",
      "name": "patrioti",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/2bfe46/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-10-29T20:26:48.939Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Katroro, kur shkoj te PPU nepermjet telefonit me Chrome si shfletues shof PPU ekzakt sic e ke postuar ne foto.<br>\nKur futem me FF56 shikoj PPU sime poshte:<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3aba0124d96c1788975024d537560b180c278283.jpg\" alt=\"FF56\" width=\"520\" height=\"360\"><br>\nMe opera 12 dhe IE11 me del si me poshte:<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/058580dafebb627e1823bc40a07305b90342659b.jpg\" alt=\"Opera12\" width=\"511\" height=\"272\"><br>\nNe te dyja rastet shfletusi theret PPU desktop, gjithsesi faqja shfaqet ndryshe. Me sakte i mungojne kollonat ne te djathte qe duhet te shaqeshin atje ku jane pikepyetjet.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 57050,
