      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/2bfe46/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-10-29T21:03:40.617Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Me FF cdo gje eshte ne rregull. Problemin e kam me Opera12 dhe IE11. Merakun per zgjidhje e kam me shume per operan se ate perdor me shpesh.</p>",
