      "created_at": "2017-10-29T21:07:38.151Z",
      "cooked": "<p>opera</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c\" title=\"Screenshot_20171029-220418-087.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c_2_800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot_20171029-220418-087\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c_2_800x450.jpg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c_2_1200x675.jpg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c_2_1600x900.jpg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9e5accb474fa03be2a8d7bdff062eae4626c904c_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20171029-220418-087.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1080 338 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>ndersa ie11 nuk e gjej ne playstore</p>",
