      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/2bfe46/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-10-29T21:11:53.408Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Opera e fundit eshta e bazuar ne Chrome (seshte gje tjeter vecse klonim i chrome). provoje me <a href=\"http://www.opera.com/download/index.dml/?os=windows&amp;ver=12.18&amp;local=y\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Opera 12.18</a> qe eshte e bazuar ne Presto.</p>",
