      "created_at": "2017-10-29T21:23:30.046Z",
      "cooked": "<p>hidhi nje sy ketij diskutimit ketu: me sa duket opera 12 nuk suportohet mire nga platforma</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://meta-s3-cdn.freetls.fastly.net/original/3X/c/b/cb4bec8901221d4a646e45e1fa03db3a65e17f59.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"350\" height=\"349\">\n      <a href=\"https://meta.discourse.org/t/support-for-opera/20218\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Discourse Meta</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:350/349;\"><img src=\"https://meta-s3-cdn.freetls.fastly.net/original/3X/c/b/cb4bec8901221d4a646e45e1fa03db3a65e17f59.png\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://meta.discourse.org/t/support-for-opera/20218\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Support for Opera</a></h3>\n\n<p>Okay, I’m fairly certain I know the answer, but we have a few long-time members who solely use Opera 12 (because Opera 15-24 do not include ALL of the functionality that exists in Opera 12, they aren’t upgrades, but a rewrite) – Plus Opera 12 is...</p>\n\n  <p><span class=\"label1\">Reading time: 2 mins 🕑</span>\n    <span class=\"label2\">Likes: 15 ❤</span></p>\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
