      "cooked": "<p>Kjo eshte Opera 48 ne Windows 7</p>\n<p>Rendering me sa di une e ben me te njejten librari si Chrome</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf\" title=\"opera1.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf_2_800x481.jpg\" alt=\"opera1\" width=\"800\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf_2_800x481.jpg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf_2_1200x721.jpg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf_2_1600x962.jpg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4c85dcc58cdb200473784fd76ae1fc3fe780a2bf_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">opera1.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1679×1011 306 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
